    "body": "Here's an same issue you can use for reference: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/22292.\r\n\r\nI think this is because the transaction you sent is a \"local transaction.\" Thus, it is still acceptable for such transactions with a zero transaction fee.\r\n\r\nRelated Geth Code here: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/core/tx_pool.go#L624-L627",
